5
00:00:12,564 --> 00:00:15,752
Sprints can be potentially boxed in two ways.

6
00:00:15,752 --> 00:00:17,518
Let's check those out now.

7
00:00:17,518 --> 00:00:21,872
There are two basic types of release or sprint plans,

8
00:00:21,872 --> 00:00:24,229
