9
00:00:24,229 --> 00:00:27,553
and these could apply to release plans and sprint plans alike.

10
00:00:27,553 --> 00:00:30,312
A scope-boxed plan defines and determines the

11
00:00:30,312 --> 00:00:32,974
features the team will build in advance,

12
00:00:32,974 --> 00:00:35,013
but the date is uncertain.

13
00:00:35,013 --> 00:00:37,146
With a timeboxed plan,

14
00:00:37,146 --> 00:00:40,304
the specific features that the plan will include are uncertain,

15
00:00:40,304 --> 00:00:43,614
but defines and determines the date in advance.

16
00:00:43,614 --> 00:00:47,041
This is by far the most popular approach used.

17
00:00:47,041 --> 00:00:51,056
Timeboxed plans, to me, are almost always better.

18
00:00:51,056 --> 00:00:53,306
Now let's look at the benefits of timeboxed plans.

19
